===Etymology===
From {{inh|es|osp|huesso}}, from {{inh|es|la|ossum}}, popular variant of {{m|la|os}}, {{m|la||ossis}}, ultimately from {{inh|es|ine-pro|*h₃ésth₁||bone}}, {{m|ine-pro|*h₂óst}}. Compare {{cog|ca|os}}, {{cog|fr|os}}, {{cog|ia|osso}}, {{cog|it|osso}}, {{cog|pt|osso}}, {{cog|ro|os}}, {{cog|sc|ossu}}.

Political sense comes from comparing a dog looking for and defending a bone and a politician searching a position.

